title: Holly Raye's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe offering on-trend food, focusing mainly on "brunch style" food, as well as patisserie. Includes some vegetarian options as well as a vegan acai bowl, and meals that can be made vegan. Limited seating and busy during morning rush hours.
streetAddress: corner of Old Perth Rd and James St
